performances.description: Starting at the 7:55 minute mark of GDTR, again very short, but a beautiful Darkness Jam.  On RT Vol. 1 No. 3, give it a listen.
Just one jam theme among many. this should be called "Kitchen Sink" jam. Has so much & all so good

performances.venue: Santa Rosa Fairgrounds Santa Rosa, CA
performances.description: Also out of GDTR, (which is very mellow), this is a very nice, (again short), Darkness Jam.  I just love this melody.
Not really a darkness jam but more of a dark star jam than what it's listed as (PITB) leads into Wharf Rat & is beyond beautiful.
The first one, (maybe not, unheard tapes are being released Dave’s Picks Vol 6), this Darkness Jam is in the middle of an amazing Lovelight.
Darkness Jam in Killer Good Lovin at a Catholic Center in Scranton PA. Rocks
Call it a "near" Darkness Jam coming out of WX report prelude you'll hear a hint of the main theme about 1:12 in & the rest is just exquisite
